<div class="hero bg-base-200 min-h-screen" style="font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;">
  <div class="hero-content flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse gap-12 max-w-5xl">

    <%# Right side: hero video %>
    <div class="hidden sm:block w-full max-w-sm aspect-[9/16] rounded-2xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
      <iframe
        src="https://customer-umftpj9wolekeelh.cloudflarestream.com/b4db1f92c0ef358622add4241742aa4e/iframe?autoplay=true&muted=true&loop=true&controls=false"
        allow="autoplay; encrypted-media"
        class="w-full h-full border-0"
      ></iframe>
    </div>

    <%# Left side: copy + CTA %>
    <div class="max-w-lg">
      <h1 style="font-weight: 900; font-style: italic; font-size: 3rem; line-height: 1.1;" class="mb-2">
        Me News
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-6">The first AI-powered Social Media</p>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        <p>
          Social media can be overwhelming.
          When did it stop being <em>social</em> and become just <em>media</em>?
        </p>
        <p>
          An endless feed of content that's just interesting enough to keep you engaged.
          We're more connected but more isolated than ever before.
        </p>
        <p>
          Remember when you went on Facebook to see what your friends had been doing?
          People shared funny, interesting moments of their lives.
          Made plans. Stayed connected.
        </p>
      </div>

      <button id="btn-google-login" type="button" class="btn btn-lg bg-white text-black border-[#e5e5e5] shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow gap-3 text-base">
        <svg aria-label="Google logo" width="24" height="24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512">
          <g>
            <path d="m0 0H512V512H0" fill="#fff"></path>
            <path fill="#34a853" d="M153 292c30 82 118 95 171 60h62v48A192 192 0 0190 341"></path>
            <path fill="#4285f4" d="m386 400a140 175 0 0053-179H260v74h102q-7 37-38 57"></path>
            <path fill="#fbbc02" d="m90 341a208 200 0 010-171l63 49q-12 37 0 73"></path>
            <path fill="#ea4335" d="m153 219c22-69 116-109 179-50l55-54c-78-75-230-72-297 55"></path>
          </g>
        </svg>
        Get Started with Google
      </button>

      <div class="divider text-base-content/40 text-sm my-4">or</div>

      <%= form_tag("/auth/debug", method: :post, class: "space-y-3") do %>
        <input type="hidden" name="name" value="Test User" />
        <input type="email" name="email" value="testaccount@example.com" class="input input-bordered w-full" placeholder="Email" readonly />
        <input type="password" name="password" class="input input-bordered w-full" placeholder="Password" autocomplete="off" />
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline btn-block">Sign in as Test User</button>
      <% end %>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
